title: Bengal Tiger audio launch postponed?
text: While actor Ravi Teja's Bengal Tiger is gearing up for a release on November 5th, all eyes are on the film's audio launch which was set for October 17. However, it is learnt that the makers have postponed the event to a day alter on October 18th. With music by Bheems Cecireleo, the film costars Tamannaah and Raashi Khanna. Directed by Sampath Nandi, the film is a production of KK Radha Mohan on Sri Satya Sai Arts banner. Boman Irani and Harshvardhan Rane will be seen playing pivotal roles in the flick.
